Democratic Republic of Congo - Ebola Outbreak 2018-2019
This dashboard displays the number of Ebola cases by health division in DRC for the current outbreak. The data comes directly from the WHO and DRC MoH dashboard and is automatically updated every week.

  • Switch between health areas and zones and between last 21 days and cumulative cases in the legend.
  • Click on a division on the map to display its information. If a health zone is selected, the graph will show the weekly data for it.
